{"tid":466736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西環碼頭擬變社區園圃　關注組反建議善用大廈街巷空間","createTime":"2017-11-13T00:00:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T00:00:47.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cba8889d2ed62be88a77c5c3be8140409390d98","tid":466736,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:00:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/132905/thumbnail/85ede41e691314587d2bfba225397fba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F132905%2Fthumbnail%2F85ede41e691314587d2bfba225397fba.jpg&h=f0567fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n政府計劃將西環碼頭改建為社區園圃，以短期租約批租予非政府機構營運，日後公眾只能進入10米闊的海濱長廊。守護堅城聯盟召集人黃健菁批評，10米寬的長廊不足以作公共空間，擔心屆時會「人狗爭路」。她又指，西環碼頭的空氣及環境不適合種植，加上碼頭與民居有一段距離，建議以堅尼地城及中區大廈間的街頭巷尾代替。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974324/xlarge/f72cbe943f2e8a29e6c1325f4d1312a8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974324%2Fxlarge%2Ff72cbe943f2e8a29e6c1325f4d1312a8.jpg&h=bc7f11de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974332/xlarge/8c5850eabc3d633da87d032ae085f735.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974332%2Fxlarge%2F8c5850eabc3d633da87d032ae085f735.jpg&h=e00785a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974337/xlarge/e2bfe47c05aa62bd97076c7ffc428d38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974337%2Fxlarge%2Fe2bfe47c05aa62bd97076c7ffc428d38.jpg&h=e895f506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974331/xlarge/20d0b0507f2e4ddcaef4f63cdad221a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974331%2Fxlarge%2F20d0b0507f2e4ddcaef4f63cdad221a9.jpg&h=fc891e6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974328/xlarge/00eec66ec68c96c6028b0972dfa41657.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974328%2Fxlarge%2F00eec66ec68c96c6028b0972dfa41657.jpg&h=f999889e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974345/xlarge/e8111c6b692bb3716c2e9601722fbf41.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974345%2Fxlarge%2Fe8111c6b692bb3716c2e9601722fbf41.jpg&h=1e1fccf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974339/xlarge/7854a37b660dc90c4d6677838fc22aef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974339%2Fxlarge%2F7854a37b660dc90c4d6677838fc22aef.jpg&h=bc337b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974333/xlarge/dbae4ebb5968c3b8f8d72f010ef9dce8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974333%2Fxlarge%2Fdbae4ebb5968c3b8f8d72f010ef9dce8.jpg&h=33ff87ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974336/xlarge/8b6173d7e9c773017e5215f0ed7587c7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974336%2Fxlarge%2F8b6173d7e9c773017e5215f0ed7587c7.jpg&h=3cec3d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974343/xlarge/2e0582c3d46d441f96b89eaeae1bd8b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974343%2Fxlarge%2F2e0582c3d46d441f96b89eaeae1bd8b2.jpg&h=18dc0bfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974338/xlarge/9213e708204fdab4e45b9839adae6606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974338%2Fxlarge%2F9213e708204fdab4e45b9839adae6606.jpg&h=144cc013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974340/xlarge/f36ebe4cbe1e6d141898dd95538e7af0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974340%2Fxlarge%2Ff36ebe4cbe1e6d141898dd95538e7af0.jpg&h=d1eeb28d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974341/xlarge/efe1c4d116377c8e0ca8e3efc4665d72.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974341%2Fxlarge%2Fefe1c4d116377c8e0ca8e3efc4665d72.jpg&h=73f62eaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974348/xlarge/b548991de9828313159fe87bd3ad7ea2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974348%2Fxlarge%2Fb548991de9828313159fe87bd3ad7ea2.jpg&h=fea0f9e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974346/xlarge/24e80f01d9f57c9e4f5e20796a742878.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974346%2Fxlarge%2F24e80f01d9f57c9e4f5e20796a742878.jpg&h=82516f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974344/xlarge/1c1c18bea771df27cdf999ef563fa663.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974344%2Fxlarge%2F1c1c18bea771df27cdf999ef563fa663.jpg&h=67776dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974347/xlarge/a12069f8048b0e936ad2c32251d4276c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974347%2Fxlarge%2Fa12069f8048b0e936ad2c32251d4276c.jpg&h=4a0b70a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974349/xlarge/8736f38220f6f50a85983a103d7423bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974349%2Fxlarge%2F8736f38220f6f50a85983a103d7423bd.jpg&h=79430523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西環碼頭除了是市民「打卡聖地」外，更是當區居民的休憩地。不過，倘政府落實將該地變成社區園圃，公共空間將有翻天覆地改變。<br />\n<br />\n根據中西區區議會文件，一般社區園圃不會開放予參加者以外的公眾人士入內參觀。黃健菁表示，香港所有的社區園圃均是封閉，不開放予公眾人士，預期西環碼頭的園圃亦無例外，意味屆時公眾或只能進入只餘十米闊的海濱長廊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974701/xlarge/d068ca7cfeb496e4fff1a7aa520f1a56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974701%2Fxlarge%2Fd068ca7cfeb496e4fff1a7aa520f1a56.jpg&h=86b29193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974698/xlarge/b9e176a97ba256a1e0644016a5c971b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974698%2Fxlarge%2Fb9e176a97ba256a1e0644016a5c971b4.jpg&h=540f1d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974697/xlarge/2f1c5d06d58004bed06fe6f455cf0ca0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974697%2Fxlarge%2F2f1c5d06d58004bed06fe6f455cf0ca0.jpg&h=a4e56e95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974699/xlarge/c44163fe3908c78eed354c0501a902ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974699%2Fxlarge%2Fc44163fe3908c78eed354c0501a902ec.jpg&h=0b89b57f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974700/xlarge/1536b387e593f2765fd24ce93a8bcf00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974700%2Fxlarge%2F1536b387e593f2765fd24ce93a8bcf00.jpg&h=20b7ab5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/974702/xlarge/df086d6db2fe47cfc7f69c6c5faa5bbb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F974702%2Fxlarge%2Fdf086d6db2fe47cfc7f69c6c5faa5bbb.jpg&h=1b5cac61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n憂心未來海濱長廊「人狗爭路」<br />\n<br />\n她認為，海濱長廊只有10米寬，只佔西環碼頭一小部分，由於現時不少人會於碼頭放狗、踩單車，部分街坊更會到碼頭散步，預料日後會「大塞車」，直言：「現時要把所有人逼到長廊內，有些人更怕狗，那他們可以怎麼辦？他們要如何共處？」<br />\n<br />\n黃健菁表示，中西區關注組曾請教社區園圃專家，對方指出碼頭近海且大風，加上空氣鹽份高及長時間日照，不適合種植。<br />\n<br />\n此外，雖然西環碼頭為不少人的休憩用地，但仍偏離民居。她認為，社區園圃應與住宅鄰近，例如天台或大廈附近的休憩用地等，以方便市民種植。她建議，政府可利用堅尼地城及中區，各幢大廈之間的街頭巷尾空位，包括位於西營盤匯安里的公園。"},{"pid":"dc7114b7f8b7e38dabffb65059baa1e4a8d907e3","tid":466736,"uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T00:00:47.000Z","msg":"黃健菁解釋，上述地點不單方便鄰居，更可避免西環碼頭的環境缺陷，使耕作更容易，她又指，社居園圃所需的空間不多，並不需動用西環碼頭的大範圍面積的公共空間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/132905/%E8%A5%BF%E7%92%B0%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E6%93%AC%E8%AE%8A%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%92%E5%9C%83-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%96%84%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E8%A1%97%E5%B7%B7%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F132905%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E7%2592%25B0%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E6%2593%25AC%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%259C%2583-%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8%25E7%25B5%2584%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%2596%2584%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25BB%2588%25E8%25A1%2597%25E5%25B7%25B7%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%2596%2593&d=ToY5HEM1M9s7pBlllVuXYgIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=f82d0a5c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/132905/%E8%A5%BF%E7%92%B0%E7%A2%BC%E9%A0%AD%E6%93%AC%E8%AE%8A%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%92%E5%9C%83-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8%E7%B5%84%E5%8F%8D%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E5%96%84%E7%94%A8%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E8%A1%97%E5%B7%B7%E7%A9%BA%E9%96%93</a>"}]}